{"tid":159361,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[大肚腩]瘦底大肚腩 點算好？","createTime":"2017-03-17T02:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T09:45:58.000Z","uid":51004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27845d1743d5c2a120bf271b62c19bbd6d998b45","tid":159361,"uid":51004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"我身高180 體重63kg<br />\n以前好肥 3年前72kg<br />\n<br />\n我個減肥方法十分唔健康<br />\n節食減肥 係最近四個月先開始做帶氧運動同埋練肌肉<br />\n但個肚腩一直都冇乜點改變過 <br />\n而家33.5吋<br />\n但一飲完兩杯水 立即變34吋<br />\n<br />\n但有時肚屙完/嘔完無胃口<br />\n個肚完全係平 冇突出黎<br />\n<br />\n我應該搵西醫 定中醫？"},{"pid":"f9c39bae44159c9f958de92bbc4f76f3ac371e93","tid":159361,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:30:46.000Z","msg":"180 72kg有幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我宜家都68 勁瘦 想增多10kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed97fd7bb6720394c67ff5361caa7a769eb0507","tid":159361,"uid":86456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"你食野 無咬碎晒 定就咁咬幾下就落肚?"},{"pid":"044e6ca1369bb3282f3186333fc31e2b6658343b","tid":159361,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:31:35.000Z","msg":"同樣情況 其他地方唔肥 淨係肥個肚<br />\n係咪叫中央肥？"},{"pid":"d86d64c8f69ade86c15e0c1bbf02b36054f40bdf","tid":159361,"uid":86456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你食野 有無咬碎晒 定就咁咬幾下就落肚?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"247884acd99c42938a56611dcb49e3930d6d3a75","tid":159361,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樣情況 其他地方唔肥 淨係肥個肚<br />\n係咪叫中央肥胖？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33aaf6dcd20750d165675dbeeca2ce62df22fd0","tid":159361,"uid":51004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><block